WEBVTT

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:48.700
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.420 --> 00:00:51.780
=Episode 8=

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:53.719
This Jumping Carp

00:00:53.719 --> 00:00:56.520
is one of our signature dishes
at Weiding Pavilion.

00:00:56.799 --> 00:00:58.159
Hope you all enjoy your meal.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:00:59.359
Thank you.

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:02.439
Ruolin,

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:03.840
