00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:05.359
It's been two years.

00:01:05.560 --> 00:01:07.640
I didn't expect Xiao Hailong
to still be the same.

00:01:08.759 --> 00:01:09.960
But Ye Chen,

00:01:10.799 --> 00:01:11.920
