00:01:22.799 --> 00:01:24.120
Good things make people feel good.

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:26.920
I've been riding
on Ms. Xiao's coattails lately.

00:01:28.239 --> 00:01:29.719
Why do I feel like

00:01:29.719 --> 00:01:31.280
I'm the one riding on your coattails?

00:01:32.959 --> 00:01:35.200
We're like a mutual support system.

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:36.280
Let's eat.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:38.040
By the way, Ruolin,

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:40.490
