00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:45.959
I didn't want to get involved.

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:48.079
I happened to read an interview

00:01:48.079 --> 00:01:50.680
with Wang Dongxue,
the chairperson of Dihao, in a magazine.

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:52.239
I really like her.

00:01:52.250 --> 00:01:54.290
She's the perfect example
of an independent woman.

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:55.799
I came back this time

00:01:56.439 --> 00:01:58.200
to join Dihao Group

00:01:58.519 --> 00:01:59.599
and learn from her.

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:03.599
Coincidentally, Churan's been
working with Dihao recently.

00:02:04.519 --> 00:02:06.319
They're so close, like best friends.

00:02:06.319 --> 00:02:07.040
Really?

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:07.439
Yeah.

00:02:07.599 --> 00:02:09.439
I've been trying
to figure out how to get in.

00:02:09.799 --> 00:02:10.439
